      "index": 1,
      "text": "Aye, aye, Captain. \n\nWe are currently orbiting [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreCooperland],Cooperland]] III and there's no traffic nearby other than the <i>Adamastor</i>, which is currently also orbiting Cooperland, but we have received word from the <i>Nightingale</i> that they detected another JumpShip at the nadir [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreJumpPoint],jump point]]. ",
