      "text": "We've been detecting signs of generalized fighting taking place all around the planet, Captain. \n\nAnd the <i>[[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreNightingale],Nightingale]]</i> has also reported that there's ship fighting taking place at the standard jump points. ",
